currently in development

uses Pimoroni Keybow to control SmartSDR via CAT interface
https://shop.pimoroni.com/products/keybow-mini-3-key-macro-pad-kit?variant=27890390696019


Left key shifts current frequency down with a configurable frequency shift
Middle key is PTT toggle ... release has a configurable delay between 100ms en 500ms
Right key shifts current frequency up with a configurable frequency shift
